{
  "stem": "8805.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I said to the Blasberg, I said, you know, let's steal a couple, to taste a potato.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we stole maybe 10 little potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not-- we took from every bunch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, potatoes grow in little bunches.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "From every bunch we took one potato.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we didn't look, and on the top was the manager from that village, and he saw us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there is no way to go, because the village we lived in where we stole the potatoes were neighbors.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we were ready with the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, girls, wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So we had-- and we had-- there was no place to run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a big valley.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we stayed, and he came down, and he said, you know, you're not allowed to-- to steal potatoes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, look at, we steal potatoes because we hungry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We plain hungry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, we are-- they used to call us [NON-ENGLISH], you know, from where we belong, like we're not Russians.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, no, you have to come to the office, and you were not supposed to steal, and you know, whatever he said.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we both went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went there, and the whole village came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they found two thieves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to her, you know, while we were walking-- it was the valley, and then you go up the hill.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said to her, you know, I said, I'm going to talk to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You hold the potatoes and slowly throw out half of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, throw right and left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's what she did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was talking to his conscience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It didn't help me nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in the meantime, half of the potatoes she throw away, and he didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
